        "description": "Decast meters will POST readings to:\n\n`{webhook_url}`\n\nPaste this URL into your Decast account's webhook settings. Press **Submit** to finish setup. Each meter that posts to this URL becomes a device with one sensor per resource (cold water, hot water, etc.)."
